title: Sam Altman Talks AGI Timeline & Next-Gen AI Capabilities | Snowflake Summit 2025 Fireside Chat
description:
At Snowflake Summit 2025, OpenAI CEO Sam Altman joins Snowflake CEO Sridhar Ramaswamy in a wide-ranging fireside chat moderated by Sarah Guo, founder of Conviction. Together, they explore the rapidly evolving AI landscape and what it means for enterprises today and tomorrow.
